code: import Swal from'sweetalert2';import{useHistory}from"react-router-dom";export default function SwalAlert(){var history=useHistory();return Swal.fire({title:"Do you want to save the changes?",showDenyButton:true,showCancelButton:true,confirmButtonText:"Save",denyButtonText:"Don't save"}).then(function(result){/* Read more about isConfirmed, isDenied below */if(result.isConfirmed){Swal.fire('Saved!','','success');history.push('/taratari-react');}else if(result.isDenied){Swal.fire('Changes are not saved','','info');history.push('/form1');}});};
